sedang menuju jalur tengah sungai...

232
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:18,685
Di terowongan selatan.

233
00:19:18,769 --> 00:19:20,646
- Jalur tengah sungai?
- Ya.

234
00:19:21,772 --> 00:19:24,233
Latura, berhati-hatilah.

235
00:19:31,866 --> 00:19:35,327
George? Jawablah. Kumohon.
